Name: Spunner
About the game: A simple endless runner that takes place on an alien world. Spunner is a first person shooter take on an endless runner style of game. You collect data chips to use as in-game currency to upgrade health, shields, unlock weapons and increase weapon ammo. There are a number of random events to keep you guessing while you try to destroy drones before they destroy you! Be careful for alien critters who try to prevent you from passing as well!
